graph TD
    U[User Goal] --> P[Planner LLM]
    subgraph RAG
      D1[Docs] --> C1[Chunk]
      C1 --> E1[Embed]
      E1 --> V1[Vector Store]
    end
    P -->|search| V1
    V1 -->|top-k| K[Context]
    P -->|generate_post| G[Generator LLM]
    K --> G
    G --> T1[Draft]
    P -->|check_grammar| GR[Grammar LLM]
    T1 --> GR --> T2[Clean Draft]
    P -->|format_output| FO[Formatter LLM]
    T2 --> FO --> T3[Candidate Post]
    subgraph QA
      Q1[Reflect LLM] --> Q2[Evaluate LLM]
    end
    T3 --> Q1 --> Q2
    Q2 -->|score>=7| F[Final Output]
    Q2 -->|score<7| P
